===Climate===
[[File:Tammisto la3.jpg|thumb|[[Tammisto]] forest nature reserve]]
Vantaa has a [[humid continental climate]] ([[Köppen climate classification|Köppen]]: Dfb), slightly above the threshold for [[Subarctic climate|subarctic]] classification. Although the city no longer (since 2009) has a coastline along the [[Baltic Sea]], it is close enough to experience the mitigating influence of the sea and the [[Gulf Stream]]. The record low temperature in Vantaa is {{convert|-35.9|C}} and the record high is {{convert|34.0|C}}.
